nodes.title: Negative Prompt
widgets_values: poorly drawn, bad anatomy, ugly, low quality, low-res, worst quality, blurry, cropped, out of frame, JPEG artifacts, error, (username:1.1), (signature:1.1), (watermark:1.2), (text:1.2)

nodes.title: Positive Prompt
widgets_values: 4k, beautiful, high quality, highly detailled, art
No need to modify prompts, the style automatically come from your images
Add as many images as you want, everything will be automatically updated

nodes.title: 2.  MODEL REQUIREMENTS ⬇️
widgets_values:
(Follow the note above before)
Go to your ComfyUI installation, to "ComfyUI/models/" and install these models in the correct subfolder as indicated below :

📁 checkpoints/
https://civitai.com/models/4384/dreamshaper

📁 animatediff_models/
https://huggingface.co/wangfuyun/AnimateLCM/blob/main/AnimateLCM_sd15_t2v.ckpt

📁 loras/
https://huggingface.co/wangfuyun/AnimateLCM/blob/main/AnimateLCM_sd15_t2v_lora.safetensors

📁 upscale_models/
https://openmodeldb.info/models/2x-sudo-UltraCompact

📁 controlnet/
https://huggingface.co/monster-labs/control_v1p_sd15_qrcode_monster/blob/main/v2/control_v1p_sd15_qrcode_monster_v2.safetensors


The models below can be downloaded directly from ComfyUI 
For that go to "🧩 Manager", "model manager", search each name below and click "install" :

vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned

v3_sd15_adapter

v3_sd15_sparsectrl_rgb

ip-adapter-plus_sd15

CLIP-ViT-H-14-laion2B-s32B-b79K

After that just click on "Refresh" And you're all set 🎉🎉

nodes.title: 1. INSTALL COMFYUI MANAGER + NODES 🤓
widgets_values:
To install the missing nodes of this workflow:

git clone the repo below ⬇️ into ComfyUI/custom_nodes/  (if you don't have ComfyUI Manager)
https://github.com/ltdrdata/ComfyUI-Manager

restart ComfyUI, click on "🧩 Manager", "Install missing custom nodes", Install all the custom-nodes in the list and then restart
